title: Building Supply: The Key to Marketplace Success
originSummary: Building supply is crucial for the success of marketplace businesses like Vinted, Ponhu, and Uber.
Acquiring and maintaining supply drives the growth and profitability of these platforms.
However, focusing solely on supply is not enough; marketplaces must also prioritize building demand and creating a strong network effect for sustained success.

title: T1's Sweeping Victory at LoL Worlds Ignites South Korea's Gaming Industry
originSummary: T1, a South Korean team, emerged victorious in the League of Legends World Championship, winning 3-0 against Weibo Gaming.
The finals were held at the Gocheok Sky Dome in Seoul, with fans filling the stadium to witness the event.
T1's player, Faker, achieved a historic feat by becoming the first gamer to win the Worlds four times, setting a new record.
